author: @jaejiju
text: I'm preparing for LET (Licensure Examination for Teachers) and lately super busy na kasi malapit na exam. Sunod sunod na din yung review sa review center (city) like almost thrice a week na. Pasado 5pm na natatapos and I have to go home sa province pa. Every time nasa byahe ako saktong 7pm, and I always, like always listen to this song. My mind is so tired, and my body is also exhausted but this song always give me positive energy. It is really comforting â€” really really comforting. It's like giving me assurance and telling me na it's okay to take a rest for a while. So, BSS my loves! Seungkwan, DK, Hoshi, Peder, and to Woozi and Bumzu as well, thank you so much for creating this masterpiece. Thank you palagi. I will do my best and I will come back here as a licensed professional teacher na. Ily!
